Why are the religious goods for Qingming

40
00:02:21,880 --> 00:02:23,600
here at the government office's door?

41
00:02:23,600 --> 00:02:25,000
That's a first!

42
00:02:25,000 --> 00:02:25,800
You are right.

43
00:02:26,320 --> 00:02:27,600
This is weird.

44
00:02:27,600 --> 00:02:28,960
