52
00:03:10,270 --> 00:03:11,030
Tea!

53
00:03:25,240 --> 00:03:26,520
What is that guy doing?

54
00:03:26,520 --> 00:03:27,800
He has been standing there for a while now.

55
00:03:31,630 --> 00:03:33,440
Have you figured it out or not?

56
00:03:33,740 --> 00:03:35,910
Buyou is expelled by the Office of Justice.

57
00:03:36,270 --> 00:03:37,900
His job in the Kaifeng Prefecture

58
00:03:37,900 --> 00:03:38,910
all relies on you now.

59
00:03:42,830 --> 00:03:44,000
Just a second.

60
00:03:44,000 --> 00:03:44,960
It will be quick.

61
00:03:45,270 --> 00:03:46,110
Zhao Buyou.

62
00:03:46,830 --> 00:03:48,190
Your brother

63
00:03:48,190 --> 00:03:50,240
is "Crafting Genius" Zhang Yong's one last student, right?

64
00:03:52,240 --> 00:03:53,550
He has been standing there for two hours now.

65
00:03:53,550 --> 00:03:54,600
Is he trying to build a new one or what?

66
00:03:54,830 --> 00:03:56,320
We have just three days to crack the case.

67
00:03:56,390 --> 00:03:57,630
Do we have that kind of time?

68
00:03:58,030 --> 00:03:58,830
Boss!

69
