70
00:04:00,520 --> 00:04:01,800
That's just an inexperienced kid!

71
00:04:02,000 --> 00:04:03,270
He's not even growing a beard!

72
00:04:22,950 --> 00:04:25,160
No case file from the Office of Justice

73
00:04:25,390 --> 00:04:26,760
