The omen is man-made.

78
00:05:04,000 --> 00:05:05,320
There are three mysteries to be solved.

79
00:05:05,350 --> 00:05:05,830
First,

80
00:05:05,830 --> 00:05:07,550
how did the fog on the river

81
00:05:07,550 --> 00:05:08,480
come into being?

82
00:05:08,550 --> 00:05:09,040
Second,

83
00:05:09,040 --> 00:05:10,640
how did the auspicious clouds appear?

84
00:05:10,790 --> 00:05:11,440
Third.

85
00:05:11,720 --> 00:05:13,160
How did Mei's Boat disappear?

86
00:05:13,390 --> 00:05:15,160
The first one is easy.

87
00:05:15,320 --> 00:05:16,670
There are a lot of things

88
00:05:16,670 --> 00:05:18,950
including the mixture of niter and sugar,

89
00:05:18,950 --> 00:05:20,000
flint,

90
00:05:20,000 --> 00:05:21,110
even flour

91
00:05:21,110 --> 00:05:22,480
that create a large quantity of smoke

92
00:05:22,480 --> 00:05:23,760
when burnt.

93
00:05:24,070 --> 00:05:25,270
The third question,

94
00:05:25,270 --> 00:05:26,600
and the most important one,

95
00:05:26,720 --> 00:05:28,160
the disappearance of the boat.

96
00:05:28,200 --> 00:05:29,200
How?

97
00:05:29,200 --> 00:05:30,200
I don't know.

98
00:05:32,480 --> 00:05:34,350
I can start the investigation with the second question.

99
00:05:34,350 --> 00:05:36,000
"Dream Pool Essays" mentioned

100
00:05:36,160 --> 00:05:37,510
that the rainbow is the sun reflected on the water.

101
00:05:37,510 --> 00:05:38,950
It appears when it's raining in the sunlight.

102
00:05:39,200 --> 00:05:40,950
The auspicious clouds are the same.

103
00:05:41,480 --> 00:05:43,040
This morning, there was fog over the river

104
00:05:43,070 --> 00:05:44,270
and the sunlight shines on the fog,

105
00:05:44,270 --> 00:05:45,760
creating the auspicious clouds.

106
00:05:46,160 --> 00:05:47,670
When the auspicious clouds emerged,

107
00:05:48,110 --> 00:05:49,270
there was a streak of bright light

108
00:05:49,270 --> 00:05:50,790
on the west side of the river.

109
00:05:50,920 --> 00:05:52,510
Are you saying that it's also man-made?

110
00:05:52,510 --> 00:05:53,720
Are you trying to cover for him?

111
00:05:54,070 --> 00:05:56,290
Can you see light during the day, no matter how bright it is?

112
00:05:56,290 --> 00:05:57,070
You can.

113
00:05:57,440 --> 00:05:58,880
I know a few things

114
00:05:58,880 --> 00:06:00,790
that burn brighter than fireworks.

115
00:06:01,000 --> 00:06:02,950
Maybe they can achieve the brightness of the light.

116
00:06:03,350 --> 00:06:04,760
Where can we get them?

117
00:06:04,950 --> 00:06:06,600
Some of them can be easily found,

118
00:06:06,720 --> 00:06:08,640
and the others are prohibited.

119
00:06:09,270 --> 00:06:10,320
They can't be easily found.

120
00:06:11,600 --> 00:06:12,640
Inspector Gu,

121
00:06:12,830 --> 00:06:15,160
my brother is an introverted and honest person.

122
00:06:15,160 --> 00:06:16,320
He will never purchase

123
00:06:16,320 --> 00:06:17,880
- the prohibited goods. - I have.

124
00:06:22,000 --> 00:06:23,460
Do you know where we can get them?

125
00:06:23,950 --> 00:06:24,600
He doesn't know.

126
00:06:24,600 --> 00:06:25,320
I know.

127
00:06:29,350 --> 00:06:29,920
Wan Fu!

128
00:06:30,950 --> 00:06:31,760
Later, you go with…

129
00:06:33,640 --> 00:06:34,350
Mo'er

130
00:06:35,320 --> 00:06:36,200
to investigate.

131
00:06:36,390 --> 00:06:38,670
Check who has bought those things lately.

132
00:06:38,670 --> 00:06:39,880
When we have all the stuff,

133
00:06:40,160 --> 00:06:41,200
we'll let you do experiments, all right?

134
00:06:42,760 --> 00:06:43,390
All right.

135
00:06:58,660 --> 00:07:03,020
[Assassination of Li Yan, Deputy Commissioner of Transport of Liangzhe Region]

136
00:07:12,160 --> 00:07:14,200
Master Ma, over here.

137
00:07:16,270 --> 00:07:17,070
Please.

138
00:07:17,790 --> 00:07:18,390
Inside, please.

139
00:07:18,950 --> 00:07:20,070
This is where

140
00:07:20,070 --> 00:07:21,000
the fire started.

141
00:07:21,510 --> 00:07:22,440
Help us decide

142
00:07:22,440 --> 00:07:23,640
how to fix it.

143
00:07:23,880 --> 00:07:25,440
How did the fire start?

144
00:07:26,550 --> 00:07:28,040
The scribe who was on duty

145
00:07:28,160 --> 00:07:30,600
