146
00:07:31,110 --> 00:07:32,350
Well, there's something odd about it.

147
00:07:32,880 --> 00:07:33,920
Zhao Buyou

148
00:07:34,160 --> 00:07:35,830
has worked here for over a decade

149
00:07:36,350 --> 00:07:38,320
without making any mistakes before.

150
00:07:38,670 --> 00:07:40,550
Eventually, he was expelled as the punishment

151
00:07:41,040 --> 00:07:41,670
