152
00:07:44,230 --> 00:07:44,830
Who's there?

153
00:07:45,270 --> 00:07:46,390
Guards!

154
00:08:00,480 --> 00:08:01,160
Who's there?

155
00:08:01,160 --> 00:08:02,920
Don't be creepy and put away the umbrella.

156
00:08:12,670 --> 00:08:13,270
Help!

157
00:08:13,270 --> 00:08:14,230
Someone, help!

158
00:08:19,320 --> 00:08:20,000
Over there.

159
00:08:20,000 --> 00:08:20,950
Hurry up.

160
00:08:28,950 --> 00:08:30,070
I've got you all the things.

161
00:08:33,470 --> 00:08:35,110
Be careful when you are meddling with fire.

162
00:08:36,200 --> 00:08:37,200
Check it.

163
00:08:38,080 --> 00:08:39,550
I spent the whole morning looking for

164
00:08:39,550 --> 00:08:40,520
all these odds and ends.

165
00:08:40,880 --> 00:08:42,080
If it weren't for

166
00:08:42,080 --> 00:08:43,000
my wide connections,

167
00:08:43,000 --> 00:08:44,080
it would be impossible to find all these prohibited things.

168
00:08:44,200 --> 00:08:46,030
After the investigation, sign the paper.

169
00:08:46,440 --> 00:08:47,710
I'll go report this.

170
00:08:47,840 --> 00:08:48,470
Wait.

171
00:08:49,230 --> 00:08:51,200
Magnesia is also on the list.

172
00:08:51,470 --> 00:08:52,670
You've got a lot of stuff here.

173
00:08:52,670 --> 00:08:54,080
Without the magnesia,

174
00:08:54,350 --> 00:08:55,640
I can't get the result,

175
00:08:55,840 --> 00:08:57,470
and you won't find the person you are looking for.

176
00:08:59,320 --> 00:09:00,880
I'm not counting on you to crack the case.

177
00:09:01,000 --> 00:09:01,440
Here.

178
00:09:01,440 --> 00:09:02,280
Sign the paper.

179
00:09:02,280 --> 00:09:03,350
The magnesia is a must.

180
00:09:03,640 --> 00:09:04,470
Sign it.

181
00:09:04,470 --> 00:09:05,440
It's essential.

182
00:09:05,440 --> 00:09:06,290
Sign it.

183
00:09:06,290 --> 00:09:07,550
The magnesia is a must.

184
00:09:07,760 --> 00:09:08,400
Wan!

185
00:09:09,590 --> 00:09:10,540
I have an inkpad.

186
00:09:12,910 --> 00:09:13,550
Judge Wan.

187
00:09:13,550 --> 00:09:14,080
Here.

188
00:09:14,230 --> 00:09:15,520
Without the magnesia…

189
00:09:15,520 --> 00:09:16,460
I'm not running more errands for that!

190
00:09:16,570 --> 00:09:17,110
Here.

191
00:09:19,080 --> 00:09:20,080
Just one second.

192
00:09:21,520 --> 00:09:22,320
…I can't get the light.

193
00:09:22,320 --> 00:09:23,080
Stick out your hand!

194
00:09:23,550 --> 00:09:25,670
And you won't find the person you are looking for!

195
00:09:26,960 --> 00:09:27,910
What are you doing?

196
00:09:30,080 --> 00:09:30,790
