199
00:09:37,350 --> 00:09:39,030
My boss told me

200
00:09:39,150 --> 00:09:41,350
that he has an agreement with the Kaifeng Prefecture

201
00:09:41,790 --> 00:09:42,840
and that I should come here

202
00:09:42,840 --> 00:09:44,030
to record the process of the investigation.

203
00:09:44,280 --> 00:09:45,710
Judge Wan, Kaifeng Prefecture.

204
00:09:46,470 --> 00:09:47,350
Do you know me?

205
00:09:47,550 --> 00:09:48,440
Of course.

206
00:09:48,710 --> 00:09:49,910
People say

207
00:09:49,910 --> 00:09:52,320
