215
00:10:08,960 --> 00:10:09,790
That's how you should put it.

216
00:10:10,030 --> 00:10:10,960
Yes!

217
00:10:10,960 --> 00:10:13,640
Judge Wan followed Inspector Gu's lead

218
00:10:13,790 --> 00:10:16,760
and helped this young man crack the fake omen case.

219
00:10:17,520 --> 00:10:19,470
That will be a great story.

220
00:10:20,000 --> 00:10:21,280
So, young man.

221
00:10:21,550 --> 00:10:23,590
What did you say that's missing from the list?

222
00:10:23,960 --> 00:10:24,590
Magnesia.

223
00:10:25,030 --> 00:10:25,840
All right.

224
00:10:27,200 --> 00:10:28,590
You focus on your work, and I'll find you that.

225
00:10:32,080 --> 00:10:32,790
Hurry.

226
00:10:33,110 --> 00:10:35,150
