243
00:11:06,280 --> 00:11:06,890
Keep searching.

244
00:11:07,080 --> 00:11:07,710
Yes.

245
00:11:21,100 --> 00:11:22,020
Yue!

246
00:11:23,670 --> 00:11:24,470
Yue!

