Don't look back.

254
00:12:06,230 --> 00:12:07,080
It's you again!

255
00:12:07,470 --> 00:12:08,840
I don't want to be a pirate.

256
00:12:10,280 --> 00:12:12,230
Stubborn girl!

257
00:12:12,230 --> 00:12:14,200
[Water Dagger, Pirate in the Jiangnan Area]

258
00:12:14,200 --> 00:12:15,320
If you join us,

259
00:12:16,000 --> 00:12:18,470
