260
00:12:29,320 --> 00:12:30,880
Here's our agreement.

261
00:12:31,760 --> 00:12:33,200
If you eat this,

262
00:12:34,110 --> 00:12:35,400
you will become one of us.

263
00:12:43,230 --> 00:12:44,350
