00:15:07,470 --> 00:15:08,470
You will

287
00:15:08,640 --> 00:15:10,150
suffer less in the next life.

288
00:15:12,760 --> 00:15:13,350
Mister,

289
00:15:13,910 --> 00:15:15,350
do you know about my profession?

290
00:15:16,900 --> 00:15:17,910
I know about the newspaper,

291
00:15:18,140 --> 00:15:18,890
but I've never read one.

292
00:15:20,580 --> 00:15:23,400
The pig-slaughtering hero returns.

293
00:15:23,840 --> 00:15:25,910
The articles in the street newspapers

294
00:15:25,910 --> 00:15:27,470
are exaggerating.

295
00:15:27,470 --> 00:15:28,790
It's just for attention.

296
00:15:29,390 --> 00:15:31,150
I don't intend to write articles like that.

297
00:15:31,680 --> 00:15:33,240
I'm a candidate for this year's royal exam.

298
00:15:33,560 --> 00:15:34,920
I'm working as a reporter in the press

299
00:15:35,510 --> 00:15:36,120
to earn

300
00:15:36,120 --> 00:15:37,630
some extra money

301
00:15:37,830 --> 00:15:38,760
and

302
00:15:39,070 --> 00:15:41,320
to write articles with perspectives.

303
00:15:41,920 --> 00:15:43,760
My power is insignificant,

304
00:15:43,950 --> 00:15:46,360
but it's still a part of the force that will change this world.

305
00:15:47,150 --> 00:15:47,920
I noticed

306
00:15:48,950 --> 00:15:50,710
your serious look just now.

307
00:15:51,240 --> 00:15:52,270
Somehow

308
00:15:52,830 --> 00:15:55,320
I sense that you will reveal the truth in this case.

309
00:15:56,200 --> 00:15:57,680
I genuinely want to help you.

310
00:16:03,800 --> 00:16:04,950
My name is Zhao Mo'er.

311
00:16:05,240 --> 00:16:06,320
Thank you

312
00:16:06,440 --> 00:16:07,270
for what you did.

313
00:16:10,800 --> 00:16:12,120
I'm Song Qiyu.

314
00:16:13,200 --> 00:16:14,270
Mr. Song.

315
00:16:14,270 --> 00:16:15,240
It's dangerous over here.

316
00:16:15,240 --> 00:16:15,800
Follow me.

317
00:16:16,710 --> 00:16:17,560
Come here.

318
00:16:17,830 --> 00:16:18,590
Get down.

319
00:16:19,030 --> 00:16:20,120
Hide yourself.

320
00:16:30,200 --> 00:16:31,560
The stability is poor

321
00:16:31,920 --> 00:16:32,920
and the brightness is insufficient.

322
00:16:33,200 --> 00:16:35,000
Flint doesn't work.

323
00:16:40,950 --> 00:16:42,440
Check the middle finger for passing away during Zi, Wu, Mao, and You,

324
00:16:42,440 --> 00:16:43,950
and check the palm for passing away during Chen, Xu, Chou, and Wei.

325
00:16:43,950 --> 00:16:44,390
Yin, Shen Si, Hai…

326
00:16:44,390 --> 00:16:46,920
This is the pre-wok ritual of a coroner.

327
00:16:47,200 --> 00:16:48,510
Lords above and lords below…

328
00:16:49,700 --> 00:16:51,520
[Yao He, Coroner of Kaifeng Prefecture]

329
00:16:51,520 --> 00:16:52,800
Inspector Gu. Judge Wan.

330
00:16:53,510 --> 00:16:54,320
Who's this?

331
00:16:54,590 --> 00:16:55,590
Coroner Yao.

332
00:16:57,510 --> 00:16:58,150
You know,

333
00:16:58,150 --> 00:17:00,150
the old Coroner Yao's son.

334
00:17:00,150 --> 00:17:01,470
The younger Coroner Yao.

335
00:17:01,880 --> 00:17:02,590
Where's his father?

336
00:17:02,680 --> 00:17:04,920
You agreed that he retires

337
00:17:05,030 --> 00:17:06,990
and you let his son take over his position.

338
00:17:07,170 --> 00:17:07,840
I forgot that.

339
00:17:07,840 --> 00:17:08,750
The boy

340
00:17:08,990 --> 00:17:09,960
is a little timid.

341
00:17:09,960 --> 00:17:11,720
He's probably stalling.

342
00:17:12,560 --> 00:17:13,320
Yao.

343
00:17:13,920 --> 00:17:14,870
So,

344
00:17:15,230 --> 00:17:16,230
how long do you think it will take?

345
00:17:16,690 --> 00:17:17,440
About an hour.

346
00:17:19,800 --> 00:17:21,080
Hurry up.

347
00:17:21,080 --> 00:17:21,840
Go find another coroner.

348
00:17:21,840 --> 00:17:22,800
None of them dares to come.

349
00:17:23,200 --> 00:17:24,560
All the coroners in the city

350
00:17:24,560 --> 00:17:26,320
are Yao's students.

351
00:17:26,390 --> 00:17:27,480
Yao said

352
00:17:27,480 --> 00:17:28,600
that his son must do his job today.

353
00:17:28,600 --> 00:17:29,960
No one else can help.

354
00:17:29,960 --> 00:17:31,270
You know what Yao is like.

355
00:17:31,270 --> 00:17:32,870
Check the palm for passing away during Chen, Xu, Chou, and Wei.

356
00:17:32,870 --> 00:17:34,680
The hands are cured up for passing away during Yin, Shen Si, and Hai.

357
00:17:34,680 --> 00:17:36,080
That's how you tell the time of death.

358
00:17:36,750 --> 00:17:38,080
Lords above and lords below…

359
00:17:38,480 --> 00:17:39,840
If he can't do the autopsy,

360
00:17:40,320 --> 00:17:41,510
how are we supposed to work?

361
00:17:42,320 --> 00:17:43,230
I can!

362
00:17:44,480 --> 00:17:45,510
I studied medicine

363
00:17:45,510 --> 00:17:46,350
and I have medical knowledge.

364
00:17:46,350 --> 00:17:47,230
I'm not afraid of bodies either.

365
00:17:47,510 --> 00:17:48,560
Is that the…

366
00:17:48,560 --> 00:17:50,560
I can do the autopsy and find out the truth.

367
00:17:52,110 --> 00:17:53,270
What are you doing?

368
00:17:54,560 --> 00:17:55,840
I'm doing your work.

369
00:17:55,840 --> 00:17:56,800
With such a huge case happened

370
00:17:56,800 --> 00:17:57,960
and so many people died,

371
00:17:57,960 --> 00:17:59,130
as a coroner, you haven't…

372
00:17:59,660 --> 00:18:00,510
Give it to me!

373
00:18:00,630 --> 00:18:01,330
What are you doing?

374
00:18:01,460 --> 00:18:03,680
What I did was a routine for coroners.

375
00:18:04,240 --> 00:18:05,390
Do you know about this trade?

376
00:18:05,390 --> 00:18:06,960
I just know that if you don't do it right away,

377
00:18:06,960 --> 00:18:08,380
you won't be able to test the poisons later.

378
00:18:09,150 --> 00:18:10,110
What poison?

379
00:18:10,110 --> 00:18:11,600
Stop meddling in things you don't know.

380
00:18:11,800 --> 00:18:12,840
I just checked.

381
00:18:13,030 --> 00:18:15,600
These men are not wearing the crew uniforms like the rest

382
00:18:15,600 --> 00:18:16,990
and they have daggers hidden at their waist.

383
00:18:17,350 --> 00:18:18,750
They have a lot of muscles,

384
00:18:18,750 --> 00:18:19,870
which means they can fight.

385
00:18:19,870 --> 00:18:21,030
It's not easy to kill them.

386
00:18:21,630 --> 00:18:22,230
Besides,

387
00:18:22,750 --> 00:18:24,720
they don't have any other injuries

388
00:18:24,720 --> 00:18:26,480
other than the lethal ones,

389
00:18:26,560 --> 00:18:27,920
which means they didn't struggle or fight back

390
00:18:27,920 --> 00:18:29,440
when they were killed.

391
00:18:29,750 --> 00:18:31,870
I suspect that they were pre-drugged.

392
00:18:32,030 --> 00:18:33,200
Even if it's no poison,

393
00:18:33,200 --> 00:18:35,200
it's some medicine that could rob people of their ability to fight back.

394
00:18:42,030 --> 00:18:43,030
You still can't do it.

395
00:18:44,270 --> 00:18:45,560
Before testing for poison,

396
00:18:45,560 --> 00:18:46,750
we need to use the black locust water

397
00:18:46,750 --> 00:18:48,960
to clean the silver needle.

398
00:18:49,080 --> 00:18:51,680
That's how it won't affect the result of the autopsy.

399
00:18:51,680 --> 00:18:52,510
You do it.

400
00:18:54,960 --> 00:18:56,440
Sure.

401
00:19:23,320 --> 00:19:24,200
What's up?

402
00:19:25,030 --> 00:19:26,230
Don't get sick for being scared.

403
00:19:26,230 --> 00:19:27,480
Let me check.

404
00:19:27,480 --> 00:19:28,440
No!

405
00:19:28,920 --> 00:19:29,720
It's okay.

406
00:19:29,990 --> 00:19:30,960
I'll get better after a while.

407
00:19:30,960 --> 00:19:31,600
I'll be fine.

408
00:19:36,350 --> 00:19:37,750
Zhao Buyou

409
00:19:38,150 --> 00:19:39,440
is interesting.

410
00:19:40,350 --> 00:19:41,900
His whole family is interesting.

411
00:19:47,510 --> 00:19:49,080
If the silver needle can't test the poison,

412
00:19:49,200 --> 00:19:50,510
then this will work.

413
00:19:50,840 --> 00:19:52,210
If the poison is weak,

414
00:19:52,390 --> 00:19:53,920
then the silver needle won't be able to test it.

415
00:19:54,030 --> 00:19:55,600
But by using hot vinegar to apply heat to the body,

416
00:19:55,720 --> 00:19:58,150
the weak vinegar will be pushed out.

417
00:19:58,150 --> 00:19:59,110
The rice ball

418
00:19:59,110 --> 00:20:01,560
absorbs poison better than the silver needles.

419
00:20:02,030 --> 00:20:03,270
Put it in the mouth of the body

420
00:20:03,270 --> 00:20:04,150
and if it turns black,

421
00:20:04,150 --> 00:20:06,480
that means there's poison in the body.

422
00:20:20,230 --> 00:20:21,270
You are incredible.

423
00:20:22,680 --> 00:20:23,750
It seems that I'm not

424
00:20:23,750 --> 00:20:25,150
built to be a coroner.

425
00:20:28,150 --> 00:20:29,350
Who released the mine?

426
00:20:31,440 --> 00:20:32,230
What are you doing?

427
00:20:32,440 --> 00:20:33,230
I just applied a little,

428
00:20:33,230 --> 00:20:34,270
and it's already so powerful.

429
00:20:34,870 --> 00:20:35,750
If I add more,

430
00:20:35,750 --> 00:20:37,270
the whole house will break down.

431
00:20:37,800 --> 00:20:38,960
You try…

432
00:20:39,080 --> 00:20:40,320
Don't add too much stuff.

433
00:20:40,320 --> 00:20:42,110
You may bomb the bridge!

434
00:20:47,920 --> 00:20:48,440
Has the color changed?

435
00:20:48,720 --> 00:20:49,230
Yes.

436
00:20:49,960 --> 00:20:51,080
The color really changed.

437
00:20:51,320 --> 00:20:52,720
Your method worked!

438
00:20:52,920 --> 00:20:55,200
Can we be sure of the type of poison?

439
00:20:55,750 --> 00:20:57,440
Why don't I smell it?

440
00:20:57,840 --> 00:20:58,990
Smell it?

441
00:20:59,630 --> 00:21:01,230
My nose has always been sensitive.

442
00:21:01,230 --> 00:21:02,150
That's why my father

443
00:21:02,680 --> 00:21:04,720
trained me to smell all kinds of poisons.

444
00:21:13,230 --> 00:21:14,480
It smells like garlic.

445
00:21:16,350 --> 00:21:17,630
Isn't that natural?

446
00:21:17,630 --> 00:21:19,480
They needed to eat.

447
00:21:19,870 --> 00:21:20,480
No.

448
00:21:21,030 --> 00:21:22,350
Never mind. Put away your nose.

449
00:21:22,350 --> 00:21:23,680
I'll see it for myself.

450
00:21:23,680 --> 00:21:24,630
What are you doing now?

451
00:21:24,680 --> 00:21:25,320
I'll cut the body open

452
00:21:25,320 --> 00:21:26,150
and check what it contains.

453
00:21:26,560 --> 00:21:27,440
No! You can't do that.

454
00:21:28,230 --> 00:21:28,560
How about this?

455
00:21:29,030 --> 00:21:30,990
Let's finish the autopsy on all these bodies

456
00:21:31,150 --> 00:21:32,720
and see what's going on.

457
00:21:32,720 --> 00:21:34,920
And then, we'll report to Inspector Gu

458
00:21:35,200 --> 00:21:36,320
and decide what to do next.

459
00:21:45,230 --> 00:21:46,030
Go check it out.

460
00:21:47,200 --> 00:21:47,800
Yes.

461
00:21:56,610 --> 00:21:57,250
Mo'er,

462
00:21:58,230 --> 00:21:59,030
did we

463
00:21:59,270 --> 00:22:00,150
succeed?

464
00:22:03,720 --> 00:22:04,390
Lord.

465
00:22:10,320 --> 00:22:12,630
Why are they so stubborn?

466
00:22:13,080 --> 00:22:14,110
You were right, Boss.

467
00:22:14,270 --> 00:22:15,440
He did it.

468
00:22:15,750 --> 00:22:16,270
Elaborate.

469
00:22:16,510 --> 00:22:17,840
It's the magnesia and sulfur.

470
00:22:18,080 --> 00:22:20,030
I read a book about alchemy

471
00:22:20,030 --> 00:22:20,990
which says

472
00:22:20,990 --> 00:22:22,440
that burn the mixture of magnesia

473
00:22:22,440 --> 00:22:23,440
and sulfur,

474
00:22:23,440 --> 00:22:24,230
the light it creates

475
00:22:24,230 --> 00:22:25,440
shins brighter than sunlight.

476
00:22:25,510 --> 00:22:26,480
Yes. I saw it.

477
00:22:26,480 --> 00:22:28,270
It's more impressive

478
00:22:28,270 --> 00:22:29,350
than the fireworks.

479
00:22:29,350 --> 00:22:30,110
I can't believe that.

480
00:22:30,510 --> 00:22:31,080
Are you all right?

481
00:22:31,080 --> 00:22:31,870
I'm fine.

482
00:22:33,750 --> 00:22:34,560
So,

483
00:22:34,560 --> 00:22:35,560
sulfur

484
00:22:35,990 --> 00:22:37,150
can be bought everywhere

485
00:22:37,510 --> 00:22:39,230
while magnesia is rare.

486
00:22:39,440 --> 00:22:40,320
Did you check

487
00:22:40,320 --> 00:22:41,110
where one can get some

488
00:22:41,110 --> 00:22:41,990
and who's the buyer?

489
00:22:42,200 --> 00:22:43,510
You should ask me that question.

490
00:22:43,990 --> 00:22:45,440
This is a prohibited product.

491
00:22:45,630 --> 00:22:47,840
It took some effort for the men I sent to get those.

492
00:22:48,030 --> 00:22:50,440
No one other than government officials can do that.

493
00:22:52,560 --> 00:22:53,680
Inspector Gu.

494
00:22:54,230 --> 00:22:55,510
We've finished the autopsy.

495
00:22:55,510 --> 00:22:56,810
There are four bodies

496
00:22:56,810 --> 00:22:58,540
that are dressed differently.

497
00:22:58,960 --> 00:23:00,440
They brought daggers,

498
00:23:00,440 --> 00:23:01,970
and they were fighters judging by their body builds.

499
00:23:01,970 --> 00:23:02,750
These four bodies

500
00:23:02,750 --> 00:23:05,200
happen to be the ones poisoned.

501
00:23:05,200 --> 00:23:06,150
What kind of poison?

502
00:23:06,350 --> 00:23:07,480
It should be the red spider lily.

503
00:23:07,870 --> 00:23:09,320
I smelled garlic

504
00:23:09,320 --> 00:23:10,480
from their mouths.

505
00:23:10,840 --> 00:23:12,600
It's not lethal if you take in just a little,

506
00:23:12,630 --> 00:23:15,110
but it will cause a lack of strength and control.

507
00:23:15,390 --> 00:23:16,150
Red spider lily.

508
00:23:16,560 --> 00:23:17,600
I've never heard of it.

509
00:23:18,030 --> 00:23:19,350
It grows in the Jiangnan area.

510
00:23:19,600 --> 00:23:20,840
I don't think we can find it here.

511
00:23:21,390 --> 00:23:22,350
No wonder.

512
00:23:22,920 --> 00:23:24,150
All right. You guys can go back now.

513
00:23:25,080 --> 00:23:25,720
Yes.

514
00:23:26,990 --> 00:23:28,230
Ban'er, don't try to help without knowing the situation.

515
00:23:28,230 --> 00:23:28,990
Trust me.

516
00:23:32,870 --> 00:23:33,510
Inspector Gu.

517
00:23:33,870 --> 00:23:36,110
Since Mo'er found magnesia and sulfur

518
00:23:36,110 --> 00:23:37,320
and the light at the crime scene

519
00:23:37,320 --> 00:23:38,680
came from the river,

520
00:23:39,600 --> 00:23:40,390
could they

521
00:23:40,630 --> 00:23:42,030
have been burning

522
00:23:42,030 --> 00:23:43,110
magnesia and sulfur on the same boat

523
00:23:43,110 --> 00:23:44,080
and created the bright light?

524
00:23:44,630 --> 00:23:45,480
Did you check

525
00:23:45,480 --> 00:23:47,200
the boats that were on the river?

526
00:23:47,200 --> 00:23:47,920
Yes.

527
00:23:48,390 --> 00:23:50,440
We detained all the boats at the crime scene.

528
00:23:51,110 --> 00:23:52,750
There's no magnesia or sulfur.

529
00:23:52,840 --> 00:23:53,800
So, is there any sign

530
00:23:53,800 --> 00:23:55,510
of smoke on those boats?

531
00:23:55,750 --> 00:23:56,720
Nothing abnormal

532
00:23:56,720 --> 00:23:58,680
on the boats.

533
00:23:58,920 --> 00:23:59,990
I have an idea.

534
00:24:00,080 --> 00:24:01,040
Maybe we can try that.

535
00:24:03,200 --> 00:24:03,800
Mo'er!

536
00:24:04,200 --> 00:24:04,840
Mo'er!

537
00:24:05,440 --> 00:24:06,150
Mo'er!

538
00:24:10,320 --> 00:24:10,870
Mo'er.

539
00:24:11,320 --> 00:24:12,080
What's the plan?

540
00:24:12,390 --> 00:24:13,390
Boats get woodworms.

541
00:24:13,720 --> 00:24:15,870
The sulfur in the bright light fuel

542
00:24:15,870 --> 00:24:16,600
expels worms.

543
00:24:17,320 --> 00:24:18,080
So,

544
00:24:18,080 --> 00:24:19,720
we'll go smoke the worms out.

545
00:24:20,920 --> 00:24:21,870
If there are worms,

546
00:24:22,480 --> 00:24:23,320
they would have

547
00:24:23,680 --> 00:24:25,990
been smoked by sulfur this morning.

548
00:24:28,680 --> 00:24:30,150
The boat that doesn't have any worms on it

549
00:24:31,030 --> 00:24:32,630
is the boat we are looking for.

550
00:24:33,230 --> 00:24:34,320
Because it has been

551
00:24:34,320 --> 00:24:35,750
smoked this morning.

552
00:24:35,990 --> 00:24:36,800
That's right.

553
00:24:37,080 --> 00:24:38,720
Even if other traces on the boat

554
00:24:38,720 --> 00:24:39,750
can be cleaned,

555
00:24:40,080 --> 00:24:41,870
it's impossible to get the worms back.

556
00:24:43,230 --> 00:24:44,390
Can I come with you?

557
00:24:44,390 --> 00:24:45,440
- Of course. - Ban'er.

558
00:24:48,920 --> 00:24:49,560
Buyou.

559
00:24:51,510 --> 00:24:53,080
Why are you here obstructing the work?

560
00:24:53,080 --> 00:24:53,960
If Mo'er can help,

561
00:24:53,960 --> 00:24:55,440
why can't I?

562
00:24:55,840 --> 00:24:57,230
I don't want you to lose your job

563
00:24:57,230 --> 00:24:58,560
and get scolded by Wen Yue.

564
00:24:58,750 --> 00:24:59,990
Do you mean I should thank you?

565
00:25:00,560 --> 00:25:01,960
You should.

566
00:25:05,510 --> 00:25:07,270
When I left home this morning,

567
00:25:07,840 --> 00:25:09,390
Wen Yue was angry with me.

568
00:25:09,750 --> 00:25:10,960
I'm worried that she might be struggling with it.

569
00:25:11,080 --> 00:25:11,960
You

570
00:25:12,150 --> 00:25:13,270
go home

571
00:25:13,270 --> 00:25:14,800
and check on her for me.

572
00:25:16,110 --> 00:25:17,440
Buyou, what did you do to Wen Yue?

573
00:25:19,270 --> 00:25:20,750
Just go back and check on her for me.

